title: IPartingSurfaceFeatureData.IGetPartingLines
description: Gets the parting lines for this parting surface feature.
returns: in-process, unmanaged C++: Pointer to an array of edges or parting line features used as parting lines VBA, VB.NET, C#, and C++/CLI: Not supported See In-process Methods for details about this type of method.
remarks:
Call
IPartingSurfaceFeatureData::GetPartingLinesCount
before calling this method to get the number of parting lines for this parting surface feature.
See
Accessing Selections that Define Features
for additional details on using this method.
